Name: Firewall Rule Enumeration
Synopsis: A firewall is configured on the remote host.
Description: Using the supplied credentials, Nessus was able to get a list offirewall rules from the remote host.
Plugin Output: By running "/sbin/pfctl -s nat", Nessus was able to get the following list of firewall rules :nat-anchor "com.apple/*" allrdr-anchor "com.apple/*" allBy running "/sbin/pfctl -s rules", Nessus was able to get the following list of firewall rules :scrub-anchor "com.apple/*" all fragment reassembleanchor "com.apple/*" all
The remote firewall is no longer supported by its vendor.

Solution: Either contact the vendor for an update or review the firewall rules settings. See Also: http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/fulldisclosure/2003-q2/0352.html.
